-- Aeroflot May Hold London Share Listing This Year, Vedomosti Says
-- B y   J a s o n   C o r c o r a n
-- 2012-06-06T04:48:38Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2012-06-06/aeroflot-may-hold-london-share-listing-this-year-vedomosti-says.html
OAO Aeroflot,  Russia ’s biggest
airline, may hold a London listing of at least 13.4 percent of
its shares worth $240 million by the end of year,  Vedomosti 
said, citing a report it obtained by the company’s deputy chief
executive officer Shamil Kurmashov.  The board of directors will consider the report tomorrow,
the newspaper added.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Frank Connelly at 
 fconnelly@bloomberg.net  